### and these by the L0 candidate code
use       L0DU        v*  L0
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# ======= the structure =======================================================
branches cmt doc options python tests 
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# ======= the patterns ========================================================
apply_pattern install_python_modules
